        <headline>Heat Advisory issued July 8 at 1:16PM EDT until July 8 at 8:00PM EDT by NWS Albany NY</headline>
        <description>* WHAT...Heat index values as high as 95 to 100 degrees.

* WHERE...In Connecticut, Litchfield County. In New York, Eastern
Ulster and Dutchess Counties.

* WHEN...Until 8 PM EDT this evening.

* IMPACTS...Hot temperatures and high humidity may cause heat
illnesses.
</description>
        <instruction>Drink plenty of fluids, stay in an air-conditioned room, stay out of
the sun, and check up on relatives and neighbors.</instruction>
